snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard in Court: Who's Telling the Truth?
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's libel court case is getting ugly as he says he was "sobbing like a child" when ex Amber Heard withdrew his rehab medicine. And she said he once threatened to throw her dog out of the car and microwave it.
